	<h1>Careers | View career opportunities currently at Vero Software</h1>

	
	
		<p>Vero is the driving force behind leading manufacturing solutions brands. Through innovation, investment and a commitment to excellence, the Vero objective is to provide customer driven manufacturing solutions worldwide with the effective use of technology. Vero is focused on providing customers with state-of-the-art manufacturing solutions, working to ensure maximum return on investment.</p>
		<p>We offer a competitive salary and an exceptional benefit package.</p>

		
			<p>We are currently looking to recruit for the following positions. Please click on the corresponding link for further information.</p>

